title: BOB DYLAN - DESIRE + Extra's (1976) AC3 5.1 Surround at 448Kb
description:
SORRY IF YOU WERE DOWNLOADING EARLIER BUT THAT VERSION WAS STUFFED.
this is perfect

Recorded in AC3 5.1 at 448kbps same as a Factory DVD
In a .iso ready for you to BURN
On your Screen you will see a picture (The famous Album Cover of course!) with
- The name of the Song that's playing, Album and Artist

1976 Desire,
and Extra's include

Blowin in the wind
Mr tambourine man
Like a rolling stone
Just like a woman
Lay lady lay
Knockin on heavens door

Using nero you can burn it onto a C.D. it only plays 2 channels
and i'm not sure if it works on all players (Leave that up to you)

Burn onto DVD will get you 5.1 and PLAY ON ALL PLAYERS

This is one of my Personal favourites.. still after all these years i think
hurricane is still up there as one of the best written songs ever..
i never had a chance when i was younger havin 5 older brothers DESIRE was thrashed along with large doses of PINK FLOYD, TOM T HALL, PRIDE and MERLE and mix that with DEREK and CLIVE's Come Again as Smoke poured out of my brothers back room!
Yeah, i was only a kid..
